            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1654600045048-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1654600045048-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your<strong> king prawns</strong></p><p>Remove the pasta dish from the oven</p><p>Add the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>king prawns</strong> and <strong>soft cheese</strong> then give everything a good mix up</p><p>Return the dish to the oven and cook, covered, for a final 5 min or until the spaghetti is tender and the prawns are cooked through – this is your<strong> one-pot creamy king prawn spaghetti</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1654600047758-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1654600047758-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1654600047758-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1654600047758-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1654600047758-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel your <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong> until you end up with a pile of cheese shavings</p><p>Wash your <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>rocket</strong> to a bowl along with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>cheese shavings</strong> to the bowl and give everything a good mix – this is your <strong>rocket & cheese salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1654600054082-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1654600054082-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1654600054082-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1654600054082-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1654600054082-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>one-pot creamy</strong> <strong>king prawn spaghetti</strong> topped with the <strong>crispy chorizo & roasted tomatoes</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>rocket & cheese salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Tear over your <strong>basil leaves</strong> and season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
      "order": 8,
